le of Yverdon.  aIssued also in print.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn German.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 04. Okt 2022) 0aTeachersvCorrespondence. 4aNapoleonische Zeit. 4aPestalozzi, Johann Heinrich. 4aPädagogik. 70(DE-588)4025111-10(DE-627)1044009000(DE-576)208959254aHistorische Persönlichkeit2gnd 70(DE-588)4044300-00(DE-627)1062061760(DE-576)209060166aPädagoge2gnd 7aEDUCATION / History.2bisacsh  aNapoleonic Era.  aPedagogics.  aPestalozzi, Johann Heinrich.1 aAebersold, Sandra, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aAubry, Carla, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aCaluori, Barbara, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aGodenzi, Luca, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aGrube, Norbert, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aHorlacher, Rebekka, eeditor.4edt4http://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/edt1 aMäder, Claudia, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aTröhler, Daniel, eeditor.4edt4http://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/edt08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertDGBA Social Sciences 2000 - 2014z9783110638080oZDB-23-GSS08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertE-BOOK GESAMTPAKET / COMPLETE PACKAGE 2010z9783110233544oZDB-23-DGG08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertE-BOOK PAKET PHILOSOPHIE UND GESCHICHTE 2010z9783110233612oZDB-23-DGE0 cprintz978311022833540uhttps://doi.org/10.1515/978311022834240uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9783110228342423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/document/cover/isbn/9783110228342/original  aEBA_BACKALL  aEBA_CL_HICS  aEBA_CL_SN  aEBA_DGALL  aEBA_EBKALL  aEBA_SSHALL  aGBV-deGruyter-alles  aPDA11SSHE  aPDA5EBK  aZDB-23-DGEb2010  aZDB-23-DGGb2010  aZDB-23-GSSc